{"tid":1632122,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"暫緩裝修商舖，轉裝修政府、議辦、黨鐵","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:15:02.000Z","uid":201464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3f36fbd4a7974ba286b260f9a35c47dd1f8390","tid":1632122,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【目標選擇原則】</span></span></strong><br />\n（１）對準政權：中共港共政權建築物、中聯辦物業、保皇黨議員物業、保皇黨辦事處、黨企、黨鐵及其他政權走狗建議優先處理<br />\n（２）先做主線：過多商舖目標導致失焦，觀感上容易變成無差別攻擊，容易被屈做打砸搶的真暴徒，前線亦會攰。<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">未有嚴重傷害或出賣抗爭者／容易被屈成打砸搶的對象建議列為支線，暫緩處理。（例如美心、富臨已經受到教訓，可以暫緩裝修）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【十八區裝修指南】</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/4/viewer?mid=18qrd4aJnY-TaYsu9jxsA6yp3zlZv9bLO&amp;ll=22.37581035920343%2C114.11057920000007&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F4%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D18qrd4aJnY-TaYsu9jxsA6yp3zlZv9bLO%26ll%3D22.37581035920343%252C114.11057920000007%26z%3D11&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=fb146677\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/4/viewer?mid=18qrd4aJnY-TaYsu9jxsA6yp3zlZv9bLO&amp;ll=22.37581035920343%2C114.11057920000007&amp;z=11</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【十八區裝修指南報料、修改】</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdvSEjtVSx9LFpB6YFYCORfcowcXbIB9iGBMAmiYi4JdmmI6Q/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdvSEjtVSx9LFpB6YFYCORfcowcXbIB9iGBMAmiYi4JdmmI6Q%2Fviewform&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=ad7ee9b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdvSEjtVSx9LFpB6YFYCORfcowcXbIB9iGBMAmiYi4JdmmI6Q/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【比例原則】</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>（黑色裝修）</strong>開放所有武力選項，<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">若目標附近有民居，不建議使用火魔法以免傷及無辜</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（紅色裝飾）</span></strong>塗鴉、連儂牆、雜物塞門口，結界魔法、紙鏈、及其他阻礙他人的手段<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">（藍色罷買）</span></strong>罷買、杯葛、負評。參考黃藍商戶地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;ll=22.371869629957626%2C114.06804799999998&amp;z=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fu%2F0%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs%26ll%3D22.371869629957626%252C114.06804799999998%26z%3D11&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpp1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=56b80de4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=10SCYSkgC9KMC_kAGtLChlGRLWVbk8NTs&amp;ll=22.371869629957626%2C114.06804799999998&amp;z=11</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01iyjRw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01iyjRw.jpg&h=28e79be9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdXOZgY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdXOZgY.jpg&h=034928b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"645ffe5c6df6857ea9ec4cdace17cdd0ef2e5c25","tid":1632122,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1631592/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1631592/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"40b6a8f42830a37f7f7fb418d07fbf32f1c00ae4","tid":1632122,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:16:56.000Z","msg":"推俾外國旅客 咪俾黨鐵賺錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632118</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"201527b5586bb6bf76140e523195d776031e6155","tid":1632122,"uid":105905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:17:22.000Z","msg":"【推上國際】的士撞入人羣呢單嘢可唔可以幫手煲大啲，喺國際上其實已經係恐襲<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631486</a>"},{"pid":"28a31536e2004b966103b356406e38c1e5f1a174","tid":1632122,"uid":110321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5468197d43413572c58f4817e741c61842d445a2","tid":1632122,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"狂推"},{"pid":"4ae279c1800d1e3b4562efaa56a3a25bba7358a2","tid":1632122,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b78f929ac39e9cbdc8816821918291469ea808a","tid":1632122,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"."}]}